Andros Diner in newark has the best food.  the best people. the best staff and it feels like home.  It is open 24 hours and i gotta say that everyone is so nice and funny that you wonder how all these people are happy  24 hours a day! lol The people are really awesome and if you cant eat-in, Andros Diner delivers! and they have pizza.. its just all around the perfect place to go and eat and chill.
